<qti-assessment-item xmlns="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0" xmlns:m="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" identifier="Q8_v15" title="Q8_v15" time-dependent="false" adaptive="false" xsi:schemaLocation="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0 https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/schema/xsd/imsqti_asiv3p0_v1p0.xsd">
  <qti-response-declaration identifier="RESPONSE" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier">
    <qti-correct-response>
      <qti-value>ChoiceB</qti-value>
    </qti-correct-response>
  </qti-response-declaration>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="FEEDBACK" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SOLUTION" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SCORE" cardinality="single" base-type="float"><qti-default-value><qti-value>0</qti-value></qti-default-value></qti-outcome-declaration><qti-item-body>
    <p>Registro del caso:</p><p>Para una fiesta se prepararán vasos de ponche de frutas. El registro de preparación indica:<br />Cada vaso de ponche contiene:<br />- Jugo de manzana: 
      <m:math>
        <m:mrow>
          <m:mn>1</m:mn>
          <m:mfrac>
            <m:mn>1</m:mn>
            <m:mn>2</m:mn>
          </m:mfrac>
        </m:mrow>
      </m:math>
      onzas<br />- Gaseosa: 2 onzas<br />Se servirán 250 vasos.<br />Considere que 
      <m:math>
        <m:mrow>
          <m:mn>1</m:mn>
          <m:mi>onza</m:mi>
          <m:mo>=</m:mo>
          <m:mn>30</m:mn>
          <m:mi>mL</m:mi>
        </m:mrow>
      </m:math>.
    </p>
    <p>Entre las siguientes opciones, ¿qué cantidad total de jugo de manzana, en mL, corresponde exactamente a esta preparación?</p>
    <qti-choice-interaction response-identifier="RESPONSE" shuffle="false" max-choices="1">
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceA">375 mL<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceA" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Cada vaso tiene <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mfrac><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:mrow></m:math> onzas de jugo de manzana, es decir, <m:math><m:mrow><m:mfrac><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>30</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>45</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> mL por vaso. Para 250 vasos, la cantidad total es <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>250</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>45</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>11&#160;250</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> mL. Por lo tanto, 375 mL no corresponde a la preparación completa.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceB">11 250 mL<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceB" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">¡Correcto! <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mfrac><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:mrow></m:math> onzas por vaso es <m:math><m:mrow><m:mfrac><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:mrow></m:math> onzas. Como <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mi>onza</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>30</m:mn><m:mi>mL</m:mi></m:mrow></m:math>, en cada vaso hay <m:math><m:mrow><m:mfrac><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>30</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>45</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> mL de jugo de manzana. Para 250 vasos, <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>250</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>45</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>11&#160;250</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> mL.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceC">15 000 mL<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceC" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. La cantidad de jugo de manzana por vaso no es 2 onzas, sino <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mfrac><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:mrow></m:math> onzas. Eso equivale a <m:math><m:mrow><m:mfrac><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>30</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>45</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> mL por vaso. Entonces, para 250 vasos, el total correcto es <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>250</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>45</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>11&#160;250</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> mL, no 15 000 mL.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceD">26 250 mL<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceD" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. El jugo de manzana por vaso es <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mfrac><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:mrow></m:math> onzas, que equivalen a <m:math><m:mrow><m:mfrac><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>30</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>45</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> mL por vaso. Para 250 vasos, se obtiene <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>250</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>45</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>11&#160;250</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> mL. Por lo tanto, 26 250 mL es mayor que la cantidad exacta requerida y no corresponde al total de jugo de manzana.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
    </qti-choice-interaction>
    <qti-feedback-block identifier="show" outcome-identifier="SOLUTION" show-hide="show">
      <qti-content-body>
        <p><strong>Resolución paso a paso</strong></p>
        <ol>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 1: Identificar la cantidad de jugo de manzana por vaso</strong></p>
            <p>Cada vaso contiene <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mfrac><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:mrow></m:math> onzas de jugo de manzana.</p>
            <p>Esta cantidad es igual a <m:math><m:mrow><m:mfrac><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:mrow></m:math> onzas.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 2: Convertir onzas a mililitros</strong></p>
            <p>El enunciado indica que <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mi>onza</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>30</m:mn><m:mi>mL</m:mi></m:mrow></m:math>.</p>
            <p>Entonces, el jugo de manzana en un vaso es:</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mrow><m:mfrac><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>30</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mfrac><m:mn>90</m:mn><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>45</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> mL.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 3: Calcular la cantidad total para 250 vasos</strong></p>
            <p>Si cada vaso tiene 45 mL de jugo de manzana, para 250 vasos se obtiene:</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>250</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>45</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>11&#160;250</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> mL.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Conclusión</strong></p>
            <p>La cantidad total exacta de jugo de manzana que se necesita para la preparación es <strong>11 250 mL</strong>.</p>
            <p>Por lo tanto, la alternativa correcta es <strong>ChoiceB</strong>.</p>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </qti-content-body>
    </qti-feedback-block>
  </qti-item-body>
<qti-response-processing>
  <qti-response-condition>
    <qti-response-if>
      <qti-match>
        <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
        <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
      </qti-match>
      <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SCORE">
        <qti-base-value base-type="float">1</qti-base-value>
      </qti-set-outcome-value>
      <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
        <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
      </qti-set-outcome-value>
      <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
        <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
      </qti-set-outcome-value>
    </qti-response-if>
    <qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-match>
        <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
        <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
      </qti-match>
      <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
        <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
      </qti-set-outcome-value>
      <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
        <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
      </qti-set-outcome-value>
    </qti-response-else-if>
    <qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-match>
        <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
        <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
      </qti-match>
      <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
        <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
      </qti-set-outcome-value>
      <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
        <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
      </qti-set-outcome-value>
    </qti-response-else-if>
    <qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-match>
        <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
        <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
      </qti-match>
      <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
        <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
      </qti-set-outcome-value>
      <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
        <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
      </qti-set-outcome-value>
    </qti-response-else-if>
    <qti-response-else>
      <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
        <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
      </qti-set-outcome-value>
      <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
        <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
      </qti-set-outcome-value>
    </qti-response-else>
  </qti-response-condition>
</qti-response-processing></qti-assessment-item>